description: Chef Everton Cameron is cooking up some high-quality Caribbean cuisine right out of his cool tropical truck, and the people of Colorado Springs just can’t get enough of all these real tasty Jamaican flavors. His authentic menu offers a selection of tender marinated Jerk chicken and pork, and Island spiced Curry dishes with your choice of meat, atop deliciously savory & sweet coconut rice. A few of the mouthwatering sides include yummy curly or funnel cake fries, sweet fried plantains, and fresh hot and creamy fried macaroni & cheese. With all this and more, High Grade Catering & Food Truck is simply the perfect choice for your next party or feast.
name: High Grade Catering & Food Truck
